    <shortlink>ux list clientside event onitemdraw</shortlink>
    <topic>onItemDraw Event</topic>
    <description>Fires when each row of data is drawn.</description>
    <arguments>
        <argument>
            <name>ele</name>
            <type>object</type>
            <description>The HTML element that contains the data.</description>
        </argument>
        <argument>
            <name>data</name>
            <type>JSON</type>
            <description>The data for the row.</description>
        </argument>
        <argument>
            <name>index</name>
            <type>number</type>
            <description>A zero based row index for the current row.</description>
        </argument>
    </arguments>
    <discussion>
        <p>In addition the Javascript can reference the 'this' scope.</p>
    </discussion>
